5000|$|Drivers {{who start}} and stop their work day at the same {{location}} {{for at least the}} previous 5 work days may drive past the 14 hour mark, for an extra 2 <b>hours,</b> if 11 <b>driving</b> <b>hours</b> are not exceeded. The 16-hour rule extends the work day by two hours, but does not extend the allowable <b>driving</b> <b>hours.</b> The 16-hour rule may be invoked once per 34 hour reset, if the 5 day pattern has been established. The driver must be relieved from work after the 16th hour.|$|R
